# Master Sequence value meaning


1     Idle  
5     StepStroke (Anti-ice)  
10    Prep  
11    Prepos on  
15    RFID on  
16    RFID OFF  
30    Ready to connect  
35    PreConn  
40    Connect  
45    Arm reconnect   
47    Box Retract  
50    End Prepos  
60    Homing  
99    End
